description: Demolition of existing part 2 and part 3 storey building to facilitate the redevelopment of the site including the erection of a part 9 and part 12 storey building and refurbishment including the erection of a 2-storey roof extension to existing 5 storey building to provide 173 residential units comprising 2x1 bed 134 x 2 bed 26x3 bed 6x4 bed and 5x6 bed units together with 5273sqm of either Class A1 (Retail), Class A2 (Financial and Professional Services), Class B1 (Office) or Class B8 (Storage and distribution) floorspace at ground and first floor level plus loading bay basement car parking (10 spaces); cycle parking and refuse/recycling facilities.
